name: Talent seller
description:
You are under curse. You don't have time to live.

But you can sale talents for time.

You can also take their talents, but someone can be without it. So, you need to be careful when you buy talent.

But if you take it, you will not take time.

How to play:

To select a talent for sale, you need to click on the talent on paper.

To sell talent, you must click on the "sell" button.

If you want to take talent, not time, you have to click on the "talent" button.
